result: R0
name: privacy_via_secure_aggregation
description: ```
Encrypted gradients:
- Client k encrypts: E_k(∇L_k)
- Server aggregates homomorphically: Σ E_k(∇L_k) = E(Σ ∇L_k)
- Server decrypts aggregated: D(E(Σ ∇L_k)) = Σ ∇L_k
```
tags: concept, 34-federated-learning

