name: definition_d7_community
description: A community is a set of nodes with dense internal connections and sparse external connections:

```
Community C_i satisfies:
  sum_{j,k in C_i} A_jk >> sum_{j in C_i, k not in C_i} A_jk
```
tags: concept, 13-agent-network-topology

