```
Q = (1/(2m)) * sum_{ij} [A_ij - (k_i * k_j)/(2m)] * delta(c_i, c_j)

where:
  m = |E| : Number of edges
  delta(c_i, c_j) = 1 if i, j in same community
tags: concept, 13-agent-network-topology

