name: definition_d7_well_separated
description: Two clusters are **well-separated** if their distance exceeds the sum of their radii:

$$|\mathbf{c}_1 - \mathbf{c}_2| > s(a_1 + a_2)$$

Where $s > 1$ is separation criterion (typically $s = 2$).
tags: concept, 11-thermal-simulation

