name: definition_313_turbulent_flow
description: A flow field Phi exhibits **turbulent flow** at component s if:

```
exists t in [t_0, t_0 + Delta_t]:
  H(Phi(s,.)) > H_critical
  AND
  lambda_max(Phi) > 1
```

