result: R0
name: definition_d9_evidence_accumulation
description: Evidence accumulation over time or hierarchy levels:

```
e^{t+1} = alpha * e^t + (1 - alpha) * new_evidence * c

where:
  alpha in [0, 1] : Accumulation rate
  c : Confidence weight
```
